  <!-- WHAT WE DO -->
  <section id="work">
    <div class="sec-kicker">What we do</div>
    <h2>Two arms, one studio.</h2>
    <p class="sec-sub">Custom AI software built for your industry, and ready-to-use digital products.</p>

    <!-- ENTERPRISE -->
    <div class="offer" id="enterprise">
      <span class="tag">Studio · Consulting</span>
      <h3>Boutique AI software for niche industries</h3>
      <p>We build the software your industry actually needs — not off-the-shelf tools bent out of shape. Working directly with founders and operators in niche industries, we design and ship custom AI-enabled products: workflow tools, internal platforms, integrations, and automations that fit the way your business runs. Small team, senior attention, working software fast.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Custom AI tools and internal products, built around your workflow</li>
        <li>Iterative delivery — see progress every week, not every quarter</li>
        <li>Deployment, handover, and ongoing improvement included</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="pricenote">Custom pricing, based on your requirements and range of services. <span>Every engagement is scoped and agreed in writing before billing begins.</span></div>
      <div class="cta"><a href="mailto:support@nevarrotech.com?subject=Enterprise%20engagement%20enquiry">Tell us what you're building →</a></div>
    </div>

    <!-- DIGITAL PRODUCTS -->
    <div class="offer consumer" id="products">
      <span class="tag">Digital Products</span>
      <h3>Tools and reports you can use today</h3>
      <p>We publish digital products — practical tools, research reports, and custom-made audits — priced between ₹500 and ₹5,000 per download, with subscriptions and custom configurations for made-to-order work. Some of our tools are free to use, right now.</p>

      <div class="products">
        <div class="pcard">
          <span class="pbadge free">Free</span>
          <h4>Dr. Mumbaikar</h4>
          <p>Your friendly web companion for getting around Mumbai — local guidance in a simple, fast tool.</p>
          <div class="plink"><a href="https://dr-mumbaikar.vercel.app/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Try it →</a></div>
        </div>

        <div class="pcard">
          <span class="pbadge free">Free</span>
          <h4>Personal OS</h4>
          <p>A Chrome extension that turns your browser into a personal operating system — your day, organised in one place.</p>
          <div class="plink"><a href="https://chromewebstore.google.com/detail/hbalkgkjjceffaekpmkpdbkkeggjfamo" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Add to Chrome →</a></div>
        </div>

        <div class="pcard">
          <span class="pbadge new">New · Launching</span>
          <h4>The Clinic Audit Review</h4>
          <p>A custom digital audit of your clinic — how you show up online and on social media, what patients see, and exactly what to improve.</p>
          <div class="pprice">₹1,999 <span>promotional pricing</span></div>
          <div class="plink"><a href="mailto:support@nevarrotech.com?subject=Clinic%20Audit%20Review">Get your audit →</a></div>
        </div>

